- content_for(:title, "Confirmation")
%p
  The file will be permanently deleted and will be listed as:
  %br
  =@efile.name
  deleted on:
  =Date.today
  by:
  =@current_user.name
%p
  =link_to "last chance to download #{@efile.name} before you delete it permanently", @efile
%p
  Are you sure you want to delete this file?
%p
  =link_to "No", @back
  =button_to "Yes",  @efile, method: :delete, :class => "errors"
